          "input_ue_unconnectable": {}
        }
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "## ZONOS2_TTS-ComfyUI Model Requirements\n\n**VRAM:** ZONOS2 BF16 uses roughly **14.7 GB VRAM** with the main model and DAC loaded before generation cache growth. Leave extra VRAM for KV cache, speaker encoder, ComfyUI, and other loaded models.\n\nZONOS2 has **ComfyUI / AIMDO model-management integration** with unload support, real tensor registration, and cleanup/reload when model, dtype, or attention settings change.\n\n**zonos2** main TTS model\n\n- 🤗 [drbaph/ZONOS2-BF16 — zonos2-bf16.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/ZONOS2-BF16/resolve/main/zonos2-bf16.safetensors?download=true)\n\n**Required model assets**\n\n- `zonos2-bf16.safetensors`\n- `dac_44khz/`\n- `speaker_encoder/`\n\nAll assets are downloaded from:\n\n- 🤗 [drbaph/ZONOS2-BF16](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/ZONOS2-BF16)\n\n## Model Storage Location\n\n~~~text\nComfyUI/models/zonos2/\n├── zonos2-bf16.safetensors\n├── dac_44khz/\n│   ├── .gitattributes\n│   ├── config.json\n│   ├── model.safetensors\n│   ├── preprocessor_config.json\n│   └── README.md\n└── speaker_encoder/\n    ├── config.json\n    ├── configuration_ecapa_tdnn.py\n    ├── feature_extraction_ecapa_tdnn.py\n    ├── model.safetensors\n    ├── modeling_ecapa_tdnn.py\n    ├── preprocessor_config.json\n    ├── tokenizer_config.json\n    └── tokenizer_ecapa_tdnn.py\n~~~\n\nIf `download_if_missing` is enabled, missing models / assets are downloaded automatically.\n\nThe loader uses the bundled architecture config from:\n\n~~~text\nComfyUI/custom_nodes/Zonos2_TTS-ComfyUI/assets/params.json\n~~~\n\n## Notes\n\n- Use `dtype: auto`, `bf16`, or `fp16`.\n- Use `attention: auto`, `SDPA`, or `flash_attention`.\n- `auto` selects FlashAttention when available, otherwise SDPA.\n- Voice cloning uses audio-only reference input and does not require a transcript.\n- Recommended voice reference: **5–30 seconds** of clean, single-speaker speech.\n- Maximum accepted reference length: **60 seconds**.\n\n## Links\n\n- [Issues](https://github.com/Saganaki22/Zonos2_TTS-ComfyUI/issues)\n- [Zonos2_TTS-ComfyUI](https://github.com/Saganaki22/Zonos2_TTS-ComfyUI)\n- [Native BF16 Model Repository](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/ZONOS2-BF16)\n- [Official ZONOS2 Repository](https://github.com/Zyphra/ZONOS2)"
      ],
